00:09.134 --> 00:09.884
♪ Well, I paid a visit ♪

00:09.968 --> 00:13.304
♪ While it's possible
I missed it ♪

00:13.388 --> 00:16.265
♪ It seemed different
yet exactly the same ♪

00:16.349 --> 00:18.309
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

00:18.393 --> 00:19.728
♪<i> Till further notice</i> ♪

00:19.811 --> 00:21.604
♪ Till further notice ♪

